is another way of revealing. Thus father, brother, sister etc., reveal relationships.<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"mentions-texteditor__content\">What I found interesting is that in Wittgenstein&#39;s Philosophical Investigations, he presented almost the same things with detailed analysis.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p class=\"mentions-texteditor__content\">The ways of looking at things completely changes the meaning.</p>\n\n<p class=\"mentions-texteditor__content\">An example from life or Mirza Ghalib:</p>\n\n<p class=\"mentions-texteditor__content\">Ghalib was once sitting with his friends when they saw that a donkey came, sniffed a mango which had been lying on the ground and without eating went away. One of his friends retorted, &ldquo;<em>Gadhe bhi aam nhi khate (even donkeys don&rsquo;t eat mangoes)</em>,&rdquo; making Ghalib retort in his witty and humorous style that &ldquo;<em>Sirf gadhe hi aam nahi khate (only donkeys don&rsquo;t eat mangoes).&rdquo;&nbsp;</em></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p class=\"mentions-texteditor__content\">Sometimes even the creator of the fundamental doesn&#39;t know what it means.</p>\n\n<p class=\"mentions-texteditor__content\">Example:</p>\n\n<p class=\"mentions-texteditor__content\">Schrodinger wrote the fundamental equation of Quantum Mechanics, but when asked about what that means, what it represents, he replied, &quot;I don&#39;t know&quot;.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p class=\"mentions-texteditor__content\">There are two principle components of money: trust and lust/greed. They have similar nature as of horses described in Plato&#39;s symposium.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p class=\"mentions-texteditor__content\">What is the best way to fix all the world problems? - Education.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"mentions-texteditor__content\">How to educate?&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"mentions-texteditor__content\">There must be some basic substructure of intelligence, need to find how to identify that and apply that to contextual methods and tools and situations as per the au